rides (e.g., lower resource limits, debug enabled)\n89: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/values-prod.yaml`\n90: - [ ] Set production-specific overrides (e.g., higher resource limits, monitoring enabled)\n91: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/values-test.yaml`\n92: - [ ] Set test-specific overrides (e.g., single replica, minimal resources)\n93: \n94: ### T008: Template helpers (_helpers.tpl)\n95: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/templates/_helpers.tpl`\n96: - [ ] Define `agentcube.name` helper with truncation to 63 chars\n97: - [ ] Define `agentcube.fullname` helper with release name handling\n98: - [ ] Define `agentcube.chart` helper for chart labels\n99: - [ ] Define `agentcube.labels` helper with common labels\n100: - [ ] Define `agentcube.selectorLabels` helper for pod selectors\n101: - [ ] Define `agentcube.controllerManager.serviceAccountName` helper\n102: - [ ] Define `agentcube.workloadManager.serviceAccountName` helper\n103: - [ ] Define `agentcube.router.serviceAccountName` helper\n104: - [ ] Define `agentcube.imageRegistry` helper\n105: - [ ] Define `agentcube.image` helper for full image reference\n106: - [ ] Verify all helpers follow Helm best practices\n107: \n108: ### T009: CRD templates - AgentRuntime\n109: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/templates/crds/` directory\n110: - [ ] Create `agentruntime.yaml` CRD template\n111: - [ ] Verify API version: `apiextensions.k8s.io/v1`\n112: - [ ] Verify CRD name: `agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n113: - [ ] Verify helm hook annotations: `crd-install`, hook-weight `-5`\n114: - [ ] Verify group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, kind: `AgentRuntime`, scope: `Namespaced`\n115: - [ ] Verify version: `v1alpha1`, served `true`, storage `true`\n116: - [ ] Verify spec schema with required fields: maxSessionDuration, sessionTimeout, podTemplate, targetPort\n117: - [ ] Verify status schema with conditions subresource\n118: - [ ] Verify additionalPrinterColumns for Age\n119: \n120: 