ard instructions\n325: - [ ] Handle NodePort service type with Node IP and port instructions\n326: - [ ] Handle LoadBalancer service type with external IP instructions\n327: - [ ] Handle Ingress with URL instructions\n328: - [ ] Include monitoring verification instructions if enabled\n329: - [ ] Include link to GitHub repository\n330: \n331: ### T031: Chart tests\n332: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/tests/` directory\n333: - [ ] Create `controller-manager_test.yaml` with deployment, service, and RBAC tests\n334: - [ ] Test that deployment renders with correct replicas\n335: - [ ] Test that service renders with correct port\n336: - [ ] Test that deployment is disabled when `controllerManager.enabled: false`\n337: - [ ] Create `workload-manager_test.yaml` with deployment and service tests\n338: - [ ] Create `router_test.yaml` with deployment and service tests\n339: - [ ] Test that router uses correct affinity rules\n340: - [ ] Test that helper templates generate correct labels\n341: \n342: ### T032: Chart documentation\n343: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/README.md`\n344: - [ ] Include chart description and overview\n345: - [ ] Include installation instructions\n346: - [ ] Include configuration reference for all values\n347: - [ ] Include examples for common use cases\n348: - [ ] Include upgrade instructions\n349: - [ ] Include uninstall instructions\n350: - [ ] Include troubleshooting section\n351: \n352: ### T033: Chart validation and linting\n353: - [ ] Run `helm lint ./manifests/charts/agentcube` and verify no errors\n354: - [ ] Run `helm template agentcube ./manifests/charts/agentcube --debug` and verify rendering\n355: - [ ] Run `helm dependency list ./manifests/charts/agentcube` (if dependencies exist)\n356: - [ ] Verify all YAML syntax is valid\n357: - [ ] Verify all template variables are defined\n358: - [ ] Verify all helper functions work correctly\n359: - [ ] Verify chart passes `helm show values` without errors\n360: \n361: ### T034: C